Durban - Any hopes of freedom were dashed for Durban businessman Rajiv Sewnarain, who was found guilty of killing his wife Shanaaz for the second time. 
Sewnarain was jailed for life following the 2010 murder of his wife Shanaaz. 

The couple had been married for 20 years. Shanaaz was shot dead execution-style and her body was found on the outskirts of Folweni (iSipingo). 
